{"tid":2150266,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 3C維修工作室偷嘢曱甴","createTime":"2020-08-11T00:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T01:13:54.000Z","uid":272569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05b09fba4034711b845272ede77a8a4787995a71","tid":2150266,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"好怕個賊知太多被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUqAUAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUqAUAy.jpg&h=0f1c5f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/K2ecBU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FK2ecBU&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lFuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=a453e479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/K2ecBU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/gxNNOS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FgxNNOS&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lFuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=52360ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/gxNNOS</a> (有片)<br />\n<br />\n//道歉聲明/ 重酬緝兇<br />\n<br />\n3C維修工作室向所有遺失手機客戶致歉<br />\n<br />\n承蒙各貴客支持，對於7月8日清晨時分，因為被爆格事件而令客人蒙受一切損失，本店深表抱歉🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n小店雖然立刻報警，但可能警力有限，過了60小時仍未可以緝兇<br />\n<br />\n暫時靠自己/朋友追查，只追查到該名賊人少量行蹤（如有更新會再update)<br />\n<br />\n當日衣著：<br />\nNew era 白色黑字帽<br />\n短頭髮（後面剷青/ 冇滴水）<br />\n衫：白色短袖Evisu<br />\n鞋：Adidas Yeezy Boost350 V2<br />\n<br />\n身體特徵：<br />\n似20-30歲，中等身形，有約174-178cm<br />\n左手戴鋼表，右手戴黑護腕，<br />\n平時應該習慣左手叉腰，習慣右肩膊揹袋<br />\n<br />\n7月8號 <br />\n06:45am 於旺角好景4樓進行爆竊<br />\n07:06am 偷取十多台客人電話/電腦後離開好景4樓手機店<br />\n07:07am 從4/F後樓梯到地下後從後門離開到後巷<br />\n07:08am在好景正門 先向右行再向左邊方向（向廣華醫院行）<br />\n07:47am 在佐敦道（A出口）白加士街￼一帶出現<br />\n3pm-6pm 到深水埗鴨寮街賣出賊裝￼￼<br />\n<br />\n如有各方人士可提供該名賊人資料，可獲重酬，因為該名賊人爆格後為我帶來十分大的麻煩<br />\n<br />\n對於本次失竊事件引起各方不便及不安，因為有貴客表示聽到失竊後成晚瞓唔着，本店再次向受影響貴客致歉，並承諾會加倍小心保管客人電話（如裝上夾萬），並努力改善服務，如日後有機會會再繼續大眾服務<br />\n<br />\n3C維修工作室字<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n另外如果有客人已經知道電話已經失竊<br />\n可加Apple遺失鎖lock🔒 <br />\n<br />\n並填寫以下資料給我們🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n型號：<br />\nIMEI: <br />\n手機序號：<br />\n<br />\n註：當時如果有留低電話卡: 請一併填寫並發送給我們<br />\n<br />\n暫時店舖電話可以正常接通<br />\n但未買新機WhatsApp暫時都未開通🙏🏻<br />\nFacebook inbox 📨 正常//"},{"pid":"e29fc9a23300517b9f61d515a282f70546a5aa18","tid":2150266,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900e334e23cc51357f0097f6445883b15ad97140","tid":2150266,"uid":326644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"仲未捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585f09dba4e50fc186879a76133afbd510707361","tid":2150266,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"又瘦樣又衰 成隻馬騮咁真係黑警？"},{"pid":"343f89ba44ab899aba6bf173b4c7403dedddbaf9","tid":2150266,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"唔知200隻有無似樣"},{"pid":"a7ed4668b88c8ff7c81677e83a97da7373e227ab","tid":2150266,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"標題歧義（以為3C有內鬼偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"552eb4e68dbda36cdb1fe035a56f2e9406a348c8","tid":2150266,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ed4668b88c8ff7c81677e83a97da7373e227ab","tid":2150266,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"標題歧義（以為3C有內鬼偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}